    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "About This Example Set",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 12,
        "w": 10,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4
      },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Rack Inventory\n\nTrack every device in your data center racks with device type icons, monitoring status coloring, and one-click access to management interfaces.\n\n### Features demonstrated\n\n- \ud83d\udd00 **Device type icons** \u2014 type strings mapped to emojis via value mappings\n- \ud83d\udfe2 **Monitoring status** \u2014 Monitored=green, Unmonitored=orange, Offline=red\n- \ud83d\udd17 **Clickthrough** \u2014 click a device name to open its management interface\n- \ud83d\udccf **Column widths** \u2014 Rack (60px), U (40px), IP (120px), Notes (35% wide)\n- \ud83d\udd22 **Physical order** \u2014 sorted by Rack then rack unit (U)\n- \u2205 **Null handling** \u2014 devices without IPs show \"-\"\n\n[Open Full Inventory \u2192](/d/dt-rack-inventory)",
        "code": {
          "language": "plaintext",
          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showMiniMap": false
        }
      }
    },
